<section class="sec reveal hub-rt--alt" id="qbcost-fixed" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">How we price</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Written fixed fee, not hourly &mdash; and why.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:72ch;">Every engagement is scoped to a flat figure &mdash; a fixed monthly fee for ongoing work, or a flat project fee for a cleanup or setup &mdash; agreed in writing before any work starts. Three reasons we don&rsquo;t bill hourly.</p>
    <div class="r-3">
      {%- for w in whyFixed %}
