    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">What each engagement ranges from &mdash; and to.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:72ch;">These are our canonical starting ranges, always shown as a range and never as a single point. They&rsquo;re estimates, not quotes &mdash; your exact fixed fee is set in writing after the free file review. The <a href="/pricing/">pricing page</a> is the authoritative list; this section summarizes the engagements and what drives each one.</p>
