      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--color-ink-mute);margin-top:20px;max-width:72ch;">Every figure above is an estimate, not a quote &mdash; the exact fixed fee is set in writing after a free discovery call and file review. The QuickBooks software subscription is billed by Intuit separately; current subscription pricing is on Intuit&rsquo;s site. We earn no commission on QuickBooks subscriptions.</p>
